---
title: Cal Smart Chipotle Turkey Burrito Bowls with Guacamole and Pickled Jalapeños
description: This bowl packs in all the flavours of a turkey burrito: Mexican-style rice, charred veggies, zippy guac, spicy pickled jalapeños and garlicky, smoky turkey! No tortilla? No problem!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-burrito-de-dinde-a-la-sauce-au-chipotle-c04cdc3b.jpg
